                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">1.危害呼吸道</span></p>
                <p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;">
                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 雾霾微粒直接吸入，最易伤呼吸道功能，可引起肺炎、哮喘、咽喉炎、鼻炎、眼炎等。</span></p>
                <p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;">
                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 169, 33); font-size: 18px;">2.危害心脏</span></p>
                <p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;">
                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 雾霾天一般气压低，空气含氧量下降，人易出现胸闷、气紧。雾气潮湿寒冷还会造成冷刺激，引起心脏负荷加重等。</span></p>
                <p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;">
                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 169, 33); font-size: 18px;">3.危及胎儿生长发育</span></span>
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;">
                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 雾霾中常含有一些过敏颗粒、重金属微粒等，吸入过量可能诱发孕妇过敏或中毒，导致胎儿发育不良甚至畸形。</span></p>
                <p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;">
                  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 169, 33); font-size: 18px;">4.影响孕妇情绪</span></span>
                </p>
